channel.title: [Album] Little Baby - Dignity
channel.description:
Hey guys! I’m happy to announce my new Album “Dignity” is now out! Currently I have only checked iTunes, but I will check Spotify and pandora later. I will release to SoundCloud for free in about a month. Please give it a listen and tell me what you think!
[iTunes](https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/dignity/1343551542)
Thanks! -Little Baby
